Charles & Colvard Warranty




             Artfully crafted, socially responsible, eternally brilliant. Charles & Colvard is the original creator of moissanite and is dedicated to offering environmentally and ethically responsible choices in the fine jewelry industry. We've been creating moissanite for over 20 years and have spent this time tirelessly refining the way  we produce this  beautiful, man-made gemstone. From our original, classic gems to our unrivaled Forever One gemstones, we're dedicated to creating better products and developing better techniques to enhance the stunning brilliance of our moissanite. Our customers expect, and deserve, nothing less.  Forever One is the epitome of created moissanite. It's formed from a specific structural configuration of silicon carbide and was previously only offered in one grade, colorless. Our new, near-colorless grade gemstone is also cut from this same high quality material, ensuring that no matter what Forever One grade you choose, your stone will be more brilliant than any other gemstone. Shop Forever One  BenefitsA Cut Above The RestGemstoneBeautyDurability Toughness BRI-Brilliance Refractive Index Fire Dispersion Hardness MOHS ScaleMoissanite by Charles & Colvard 2.65-2.69 0.104 9.25 ExcellentDiamond 2.42 0.044 10 Excellent*Ruby 1.77 0.018 9 Excellent**Sapphire 1.77 0.018 9 Excellent**Emerald 1.58 0.014 7.5 Good to Poor *In cleavage direction, toughness is "good" **Except twinned stonesMORE FIRE Dispersion 0.104THE MOST BRILLIANCE Refractive index 2.65-2.69GUARANTEED TO LAST Excellent toughnessMADE FOR DAILY WEAR MOHS Scale 9.25Gemstone Comparison ChartMoissanite by Charles and ColvardBeauty BRI - Brilliance Refractive Index 2.65-2.69 Fire Dispersion 0.104 Hardness  MOHS Scale 9.25Durability Toughness ExcellentDiamondBeauty BRI - Brilliance Refractive Index 2.42 Fire Dispersion 0.044 Hardness  MOHS Scale 10Durability Toughness ExcellentRubyBeauty BRI - Brilliance Refractive Index 1.77 Fire Dispersion 0.018 Hardness  MOHS Scale 9Durability Toughness ExcellentSapphireBeauty BRI - Brilliance Refractive Index 1.77 Fire Dispersion 0.018 Hardness  MOHS Scale 9Durability Toughness ExcellentEmeraldBeauty BRI - Brilliance Refractive Index 1.58 Fire Dispersion 0.014 Hardness  MOHS Scale 7.5Durability Toughness Good to Poor *In cleavage direction, toughness is "good"  ** Except twinned stones  A cut above the rest. Shop by shape.  Cushion > Square > Round > Oval > Asscher > Hearts & Arrows > Emerald > Pear > Radiant > Princess >  The Four C's of MoissaniteHeld to a higher standard.  CutAdmire facets shaped by experts,and oh-so-pleasing to the eye. ColorSelect a grade that’s colorless,or one with the slightest icy hue. CharacterChoose the stone that’s made for you, and make it your own. ConscienceKnow that it's made with our ethics and earth in mind.  Charles & Colvard WarrantyBrilliance We Guarantee Will Never FadeEvery Charles & Colvard created gem is guaranteed to remain as beautiful as the day you bought it. Whether for an engagement ring, Mother’s Day present, or a gift to yourself — it comes with a limited lifetime warranty that protects against damage to the stone and any changes in color, clarity or brilliance. Learn More About Our Warranty Made with care for those of us who choose with care.Charles & Colvard prioritizes environmental and ethical responsibility in the creation of our moissanite. The arresting beauty and superior quality of our gems, paired with our commitment to our principles, makes Forever One a superior sustainable and conflict-free gemstone. Our Story >     






